        <div class="c-article-body">
            <div class="c-article-section__content c-article-section__content--standfirst u-text-bold" lang="en"><p>Quantum machine learning is being actively explored to assess whether quantum resources can enhance learning and inference, yet major obstacles remain. Here, we discuss pressing challenges and outline potential pathways toward future practical applications.</p></div>

            
                
